accept-ert-window-title = Emergency Response Team Recruitment!
accept-ert-window-prompt-text-part = Are you ready to become part of an ERT squad? If you are not sure, it is better to say NO!

ert-accept-message = Attention! We have received a request for an Emergency Response Team. The request has been approved! Please stand by.
ert-deny-message = Attention! We have received a request for an Emergency Response Team. The request has been denied! We cannot deploy it at this time.
ert-wait-message = An Emergency Response Team request has been received. Awaiting decision.
